Universal compiling scripts for FRC

Requirements:
 - The current version requires WindRiver files to be present on the
   system.
 - Future versions might package the required files

Installation:
 - Add the "makefiles" folder to the system PATH
 - Modify "makefiles/ucpp-settings"

Usage:
 - ucpp-init -t <team-number>
        Configures the current directory as an FRC C++ project
		for your team.
 - ucpp-configure <command>
   		Generates a Makefile for your project
 - cd PPC603gnu && make -f Makefile_linux